{"tid":1099024,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"遲覆whatsapp咪遲覆囉 個個好似你咁得閒咩","createTime":"2019-04-09T13:20:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T17:05:01.000Z","uid":89105,"like":22,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dd539d07c1d693aceac7e8f774bea9a573f34af8","tid":1099024,"uid":89105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T13:20:54.000Z","msg":"擺到明唔得閒覆 或者唔想覆 <br />\n所以有時遲幾分/遲幾粒鐘覆都會<br />\n你長期游手好閒得閒秒回 <br />\n唔撚代表人地都得閒秒回你呀<br />\n遲幾分鐘覆 又話我係咪好忙 又話自己似自言自語<br />\n係呀係呀 傻hi 你自己知就好啦    長期話人遲覆 <br />\n個撚個似你咁無聊淨係識用電話咩  <br />\n點解你咁撚得閒架    <br />\n<br />\n有時擺到明遲覆架啦 <br />\n以為自己邊個 勁厚臉皮炸我機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌你老母你既出現令我知道 <br />\n原來呢個世界係有人咁撚煩架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無人好憎人出聲成日話你遲覆 / 俾說話你聽<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解啲人可以咁撚厚臉皮   <br />\n<br />\n我好想大叫 屌你老母阿！但凡事留一線 日後好相見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b08a26d3f3278652e90f1700bf74d9092c9ef513","tid":1099024,"uid":89105,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T13:24:57.000Z","msg":"有啲人真係好撚有自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2339a4014757cd5b4fa46d1c515d91b3f1a1fbe1","tid":1099024,"uid":154871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T13:28:11.000Z","msg":"你係咪我男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed6fce07c712b606003243c15ea9ca00dc63489","tid":1099024,"uid":105396,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T13:30:21.000Z","msg":"有個朋友好撚煩<br />\n<br />\n「你星期日得唔得閒？」<br />\n「喂」<br />\n「喂」<br />\n「又做乜鳩」<br />\n<br />\n真係好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔得閒覆你啫 使唔使係咁炸我機<br />\n之後我同佢講話唔得閒出唔到嚟 就會應我：<br />\n<br />\n「你又搞乜鳩呀」<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母你估個個好似你咁得閒廢喺屋企啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家老馮要同你出去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cdb61f1fae759b10400f02163895ee329805400","tid":1099024,"uid":161734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T13:42:33.000Z","msg":"咁緊要就打電話啦 係咁喺個gp到@我做乜撚嘢<br />\n<br />\n錄音撚又係仆街嚟 錄撚埋啲廢話 又要聽先知你咩事 一陣唔得閒覆又話已讀"},{"pid":"b9f3820f8abfca83dc45a82dddc34d91438342d8","tid":1099024,"uid":96815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T13:58:31.000Z","msg":"岩岩先屌完個煩膠 唔覆佢就係咁話我搵其他人唔搵佢 嬲撚到即刻問佢邊位 下下做野都要同你交代啊？"},{"pid":"8e28cbb1e2564358710eef27ddbae88a8ba29de0","tid":1099024,"uid":148053,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T14:02:35.000Z","msg":"真係戇鳩，whatsapp既原意就係我有事揾你，但又唔急，等你得閒先覆。炸人機嗰啲好心打電話啦"},{"pid":"287c086a5e59789041c54f502b88007fcc43aa76","tid":1099024,"uid":89105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2339a4014757cd5b4fa46d1c515d91b3f1a1fbe1","tid":1099024,"uid":154871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T13:28:11.000Z","msg":"你係咪我男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T14:47:26.000Z","msg":"男女朋友起碼都有啲地位有權出下聲"},{"pid":"52eb62d20218648a57bd30cc5afdc97fcca501d9","tid":1099024,"uid":89105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ed6fce07c712b606003243c15ea9ca00dc63489","tid":1099024,"uid":105396,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T13:30:21.000Z","msg":"有個朋友好撚煩<br />\n<br />\n「你星期日得唔得閒？」<br />\n